# DB

역정규화 데이터는 Firebase Cloud Functions의 서버 리스너로 등록해서 관리

읽기/쓰기 비율을 감안해서 정규화/역정규화 선택

즉 상태 변경보다 조회가 압도적으로 많은 경우 역정규화

## Users 컬렉션

**[Collection: Users] → Get/Set**

- **[Document: {uid}]**
    - nickname: "홍길동" (String)
    - profile_image_url: “http://~~” (String)
    - status: "심심함" (String)
    - is_sharing: true (Boolean)
    - is_online: true (Boolean)
    - fcm_token: "token_abc123" (String)
    - last_active: 2026-05-07 19:00:00 (Timestamp)
    - friendUids: [”uid1”, “uid2”] : (Array) ← 역정규화
    - **[Sub-Collection: Friendships] → Silent Push**
        - **[Document: {friend_uid}]**
            - nickname: "홍길동" (String) - 역정규화
            - profile_image_url: “http://~~” (String) - 역정규화
            - status: "심심함" (String) - 역정규화
            - is_online: true (Boolean)
            - friendship_status: "ACCEPTED" (String)
            - created_at: 2026-04-20 10:30:00 (Timestamp)
- **[Collection: Live] → 실시간 구독**
    - **[Document: {uid}]**
        - profile_image_url: “http://~~” (String) → 역정규화
        - is_sharing: true (Boolean) → 역정규화
        - is_online: true (Boolean) → 역정규화
        - location: [37.5665, 126.9780] (GeoPoint)
        - updated_at: 2026-04-20 10:30:00 (Timestamp) → 마지막 업데이트
- **[Collection: Notifications] → Get/Set //바로 못 읽은 경우**
    - **[Document: {noti_id}]**
        - **type**: "WALKIE" (String)
        - **sender_id**: "sender_uid" (String)
        - **sender_name**: "홍길동" (String)
        - **content**: "음성 메시지가 도착했습니다." (String)
        - **audio_url**: "https://firebasestorage.../audio.m4a" (String)
        - **is_read**: false (Boolean)
        - **created_at**: 2026-05-09 12:50:00 (Timestamp)
- **[Collection: VoiceMessages] → 실시간 구독 //무전 바로 받은 경우**
    - **[Document: {sender_uid}]**
    - **sender_id**: "sender_uid_123" (String)
    - **receiver_id**: "receiver_uid_456" (String)
    - **voice_url**: "https://firebasestorage.../audio.m4a" (String)
    - **duration**: 5 (Number)
    - **is_read**: false (Boolean)
    - **sent_at**: 2026-05-09 12:48:00 (Timestamp)

